```mermaid
flowchart TD

  ST([Start]) --> LG{Logged in?}

  LG -- "No" --> LG1[Login screen<br/>Enter ID, password, OTP]
  LG1 --> LG2{Login success?}
  LG2 -- "Yes" --> HM[Home]

  LG -- "Yes" --> HM

  HM --> SYM[Select symbol<br/>From Watchlist / Search]
  SYM --> S0[Open Sell order form]
  S0 --> SPROD{Product type?}

  SPROD -- "Delivery" --> SD_HOLD{Has holdings?}

  SD_HOLD -- "No" --> SD_TODAY{Has today's buy position?}

  %% No Holdings + No Today Position = Rejection
  SD_TODAY -- "No" --> SD_REJECT[
    Cannot place Delivery Sell<br/>
    No holdings and no today's buy<br/>
    Show validation / RMS error
  ]

  SD_REJECT --> SD_OB[Add entry in Order Book<br/>Status: Rejected]

  SD_OB --> END([End])
